snippet.title: Paranoia - Liam Hemsworth Featurette
snippet.description:
Paranoia - Liam Hemsworth Featurette

Paranoia directed by Robert Luketic and starring Liam Hemsworth, Amber Heard

An entry-level employee at a powerful corporation finds himself occupying a corner office, but at a dangerous price: he must spy on his boss's old mentor to secure for him a multi-billion dollar advantage.

Release Date: August 16th, 2013
Director: Robert Luketic
Cast: Gary Oldman, Liam Hemsworth, Amber Heard, Harrison Ford, Embeth Davidtz
Genre: Thriller, Drama
